Class DynamicSqlModelGenerator

java.lang.Object
org.mybatis.generator.codegen.AbstractGenerator
org.mybatis.generator.codegen.AbstractJavaGenerator
org.mybatis.generator.runtime.dynamic.sql.DynamicSqlModelGenerator
public class DynamicSqlModelGenerator extends AbstractJavaGenerator
This model generator builds a flat model with default constructor and getters/setters. It does not support the immutable model, or constructor based attributes.
